{{/*
  FEVER EVENTS — Post-Event Follow-up
  Master-Template fuer Listmonk-Campaigns.

  Zwei Variablen-Klassen:

  1) Build-time Replace (das Sync-Script ersetzt diese VOR dem POST an Listmonk):
     {{EVENT_NAME}}          z.B. "Polterparty Jens & Svenja"
     {{EVENT_DATE_DE}}       z.B. "15. Mai 2026"
     {{SPOTIFY_PLAYLIST_URL}} Spotify-Playlist-Link
     {{GOOGLE_REVIEW_URL}}   z.B. https://g.page/r/...
     {{PERSONAL_PARAGRAPHS}} Polter-/Hochzeit-/Geburtstag-spezifischer Text (HTML-<p>-Bloecke)
     {{HERO_IMG_URL}}        optional: Bild-URL ueber dem Content (kann leer sein, dann wird Hero-Block ausgeblendet)
     {{MOOD_IMG_URL}}        optional: Stimmungsbild ueber der Spotify-Karte

  2) Listmonk-runtime (Go-Templates, Listmonk fuellt pro Empfaenger aus):
     {{ .Subscriber.Attribs.firstname }} Vorname (vom Sync-Script als Attribute gesetzt)
     {{ .Subscriber.Email }}              E-Mail des Empfaengers
     {{ UnsubscribeURL }}                 Automatischer Listmonk-Unsubscribe-Link
     {{ TrackLink "URL" }}                Click-Tracking-Wrapper (optional)
*/}}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="color-scheme" content="dark only">
  <meta name="supported-color-schemes" content="dark only">
  <title>Danke für {{EVENT_NAME}} — FEVER EVENTS</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#100726;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:#ffffff;">

  <div style="display:none;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;color:transparent;">
    Die Playlist auf Spotify &amp; ein kleiner Wunsch zum Schluss.
  </div>

  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color:#100726;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding:32px 16px 48px 16px;">

        <table role="presentation" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="max-width:600px;width:100%;">

          <!-- Hero / Branding -->
          <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding:8px 0 24px 0;">
              <div style="display:inline-block;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:999px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#D71362 0%,#CB01F3 100%);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#ffffff;">
                FEVER EVENTS
              </div>
              <h1 style="margin:18px 0 0 0;font-size:34px;line-height:1.1;font-weight:900;color:#ffffff;letter-spacing:-0.02em;">
                Was für eine Nacht.
              </h1>
              <div style="margin:14px auto 0 auto;height:3px;width:64px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#D71362 0%,#CB01F3 100%);border-radius:2px;"></div>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Optionales Hero-Bild -->
          {{if (ne "{{HERO_IMG_URL}}" "")}}
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:8px 0 8px 0;">
              <img src="{{HERO_IMG_URL}}" alt="{{EVENT_NAME}}" width="600" style="display:block;width:100%;max-width:600px;height:auto;border-radius:12px;border:0;outline:none;">
            </td>
          </tr>
          {{end}}

          <!-- Content-Karte -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color:#1a0d36;border-radius:16px;padding:36px 32px;box-shadow:0 24px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);">

              <p style="margin:0 0 10px 0;font-size:18px;font-weight:600;color:#ffffff;">
                Hey {{ .Subscriber.Attribs.firstname }},
              </p>

              {{PERSONAL_PARAGRAPHS}}

              <!-- Optionales Mood-Bild -->
              {{if (ne "{{MOOD_IMG_URL}}" "")}}
              <p style="margin:24px 0 0 0;">
                <img src="{{MOOD_IMG_URL}}" alt="Stimmung der Nacht" width="536" style="display:block;width:100%;max-width:536px;height:auto;border-radius:12px;border:0;outline:none;">
              </p>
              {{end}}

              <!-- Spotify-Karte -->
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin-top:32px;background-color:#100726;border:1px solid rgba(215,19,98,0.35);border-radius:14px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:24px 24px 8px 24px;">
                    <p style="margin:0;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#00CFC8;">
                      Die Setlist der Nacht
                    </p>
                    <p style="margin:8px 0 0 0;font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#ffffff;line-height:1.3;">
                      {{EVENT_NAME}} — Live-Mix
                    </p>
                    <p style="margin:8px 0 0 0;font-size:14px;color:#b9aed6;line-height:1.6;">
                      Komplett chronologisch, jeder Track in der Reihenfolge wie er lief. Zum Nachhören, Mitsingen oder für die After-Party im Auto.
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td align="left" style="padding:18px 24px 26px 24px;">
                    <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td style="border-radius:10px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#D71362 0%,#CB01F3 100%);">
                          <a href="{{ TrackLink "{{SPOTIFY_PLAYLIST_URL}}" }}" style="display:inline-block;padding:14px 24px;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.01em;">
                            Playlist auf Spotify öffnen &rarr;
                          </a>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Google-Review-CTA -->
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin-top:28px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:24px;background-color:rgba(0,207,200,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(0,207,200,0.35);border-radius:14px;">
                    <p style="margin:0;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#00CFC8;">
                      Kleine Bitte zum Schluss
                    </p>
                    <p style="margin:8px 0 0 0;font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;line-height:1.4;">
                      Hat die Nacht gerockt? Dann lass mir gerne eine Bewertung da.
                    </p>
                    <p style="margin:10px 0 18px 0;font-size:14px;color:#cfc6e6;line-height:1.6;">
                      Zwei, drei Sätze auf Google helfen riesig — gerade als selbstständiger DJ. Versprochen: dauert keine zwei Minuten.
                    </p>
                    <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td style="border-radius:10px;background-color:#00CFC8;">
                          <a href="{{ TrackLink "{{GOOGLE_REVIEW_URL}}" }}" style="display:inline-block;padding:14px 24px;font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#100726;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.01em;">
                            Auf Google bewerten &rarr;
                          </a>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="margin:32px 0 0 0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:#e8e3f5;">
                Falls du selbst mal was zu feiern hast — Geburtstag, Hochzeit, Firmenfeier — <a href="https://www.fever-events.de" style="color:#00CFC8;text-decoration:underline;">www.fever-events.de</a> ist immer der richtige Ort, um Hallo zu sagen.
              </p>

              <p style="margin:18px 0 0 0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:#e8e3f5;">
                Bis bald auf der Tanzfläche,<br>
                <strong style="color:#ffffff;">Toby</strong>
                <span style="color:#b9aed6;"> &middot; DJ tonicfresh</span>
              </p>

            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding:28px 16px 0 16px;">
              <p style="margin:0;font-size:12px;color:#7a6d99;line-height:1.7;">
                <strong style="color:#cfc6e6;">FEVER EVENTS</strong> &middot; Toby Fieberling &middot; DJ tonicfresh<br>
                <a href="mailto:info@fever-events.de" style="color:#7a6d99;text-decoration:underline;">info@fever-events.de</a>
                &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;
                <a href="https://www.fever-events.de" style="color:#7a6d99;text-decoration:underline;">www.fever-events.de</a>
              </p>
              <p style="margin:10px 0 0 0;font-size:11px;color:#5a4f78;line-height:1.6;">
                <a href="https://www.fever-events.de/impressum" style="color:#5a4f78;text-decoration:underline;">Impressum</a>
                &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;
                <a href="https://www.fever-events.de/privacy-policy" style="color:#5a4f78;text-decoration:underline;">Datenschutz</a>
                &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;
                <a href="{{ UnsubscribeURL }}" style="color:#5a4f78;text-decoration:underline;">Abmelden</a>
              </p>
              <p style="margin:12px 0 0 0;font-size:11px;color:#5a4f78;line-height:1.6;">
                Du bekommst diese Mail einmalig nach {{EVENT_NAME}} ({{EVENT_DATE_DE}}).
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

</body>
</html>
